      "description": "This exceptional vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, it presents in pristine condition with flawless exterior surfaces and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector, this unit offers unparalleled mechanical integrity and aesthetic perfection. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark example of the model.",
