    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s sparkling clean and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no stories, just a perfect ride waiting for its next home. If you've been looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is the one! Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
