    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a meticulously maintained Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The limited-slip differential remains tight, providing optimal torque vectoring. Every bushing, seal, and fluid has been serviced to factory specifications. The chassis displays zero fatigue, and the paint finish retains its original factory depth. This is a turn-key performance icon for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
