    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this breathtaking specimen. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like luster thanks to a multi-stage paint correction and premium ceramic coating; there isn't a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish to be found. Inside, the cabin retains that distinctive new-car aroma, with the hand-stitched leather seats showing absolutely zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the advanced driver-assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having followed a strict maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships with all records organized in a comprehensive binder. The engine bay is remarkably clean, and the undercarriage remains spotless, reflecting its life as a pampered, garage-kept treasure. This is a time-capsule quality vehicle for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the best.",
